        "compareChart": {
            "value": "<mas-compare-chart expanded-groups=\"1\"><span slot=\"compare-features\">Compare Features</span><div name=\"adobe-apps\"><h4>Adobe apps</h4><p name=\"seamless-integration-across-adobe-apps\">Seamless integration across Adobe apps <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign, Firefly, Acrobat and Lightroom\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"boost-your-creativity-with-photoshop\">Boost your creativity with Photoshop <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Full access to Photoshop on web and mobile, in addition to Adobe Express Premium\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"adobe-firefly-pro\">Adobe Firefly Pro <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Create images, video, audio, vector graphics, Firefly Boards, and use latest commercially safe Firefly AI models\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"integration-with-adobe-experience-manager-workfront-and-genstudio\">Integration with Adobe Experience Manager, Workfront, and GenStudio <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"For performance marketing\">ℹ️</a></p></div><div name=\"templates-and-design-assets\"><h4>Templates and design assets</h4><p name=\"professionally-designed-templates\">Professionally designed templates <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Static, motion, and video templates\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"template-recommendations\">Template recommendations <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Preview your photo in editable templates that match the photo context\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"adobe-stock-photos\">Adobe Stock photos</p><p name=\"adobe-stock-videos\">Adobe Stock videos</p><p name=\"adobe-stock-audiomusic\">Adobe Stock audio/music</p><p name=\"adobe-stock-sound-effects\">Adobe Stock sound effects</p><p name=\"adobe-stock-backgrounds\">Adobe Stock backgrounds</p><p name=\"adobe-stock-design-assets\">Adobe Stock design assets <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Illustrations, brushes, textures, frames, and more\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"adobe-stock-icons\">Adobe Stock icons</p><p name=\"basic-shapes\">Basic Shapes</p></div><div name=\"generative-ai\"><h4>Generative AI</h4><p name=\"ai-assistant-beta\">AI Assistant Beta <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Prompt-anything, edit-everything\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"generate-presentations\">Generate Presentations <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Turn documents into presentations in minutes\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"generative-credits\">Generative credits</p><p name=\"generate-images-text-effects-templates--more\">Generate images, text effects, templates &amp; more</p><p name=\"insert--remove-objects\">Insert &amp; Remove Objects</p><p name=\"commercial-use\">Commercial Use <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Features designed to be commercially safe, powered by Adobe Firefly generative AI\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"partner-generative-ai-models\">Partner generative AI models <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Access partner models in Firefly such as Google, OpenAI, Flux, and more\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"generate-5-second-videos\">Generate 5-second videos</p><p name=\"adobe-firefly-boards\">Adobe Firefly Boards</p></div><div name=\"photo-and-design\"><h4>Photo and design</h4><p name=\"erase\">Erase</p><p name=\"photo-adjustments-and-effects\">Photo Adjustments and Effects <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Adjust contrast, shadows, saturation, effects, and blend modes, powered by Photoshop\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"start-from-photos\">Start from photos <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Start from JPG, PNG, PSD, and more\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"adobe-fonts\">Adobe Fonts</p><p name=\"font-recommendations\">Font recommendations <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Recommendations for fonts that match your design\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"add-and-sync-psd-and-ai-files\">Add and sync .psd and .ai files <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Edits made in Photoshop or Illustrator sync without reimporting\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"export-in-jpeg-png-pdf-gif-ppt\">Export in JPEG, PNG, PDF, GIF, PPT</p><p name=\"export-as-png-with-transparent-background\">Export as PNG with transparent background</p><p name=\"draw-and-paint-with-85-brushes-and-coloring-pages\">Draw and paint with 85+ brushes and coloring pages</p></div><div name=\"video-and-motion\"><h4>Video and motion</h4><p name=\"drag-and-drop-video-creation\">Drag-and-drop video creation</p><p name=\"remove-video-background\">Remove video background</p><p name=\"animate-all\">Animate All <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Automatically apply motion to your entire design\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"dynamic-animations\">Dynamic Animations <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Add physics-based animation to photos, videos, text, shapes, and icons\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"record-voiceover-and-video-directly-in-app\">Record voiceover and video directly in-app</p><p name=\"video-transitions\">Video transitions</p><p name=\"video-length\">Video length</p><p name=\"export-in-4k\">Export in 4K</p><p name=\"enhance-speech\">Enhance Speech</p><p name=\"tiktok-symphony-assistant-add-on\">TikTok Symphony Assistant Add-on <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"1M+ songs and sounds from TikTok’s Commercial Music Library\">ℹ️</a></p></div><div name=\"quick-actions\"><h4>Quick Actions</h4><p name=\"remove-image-background\">Remove Image Background</p><p name=\"resize-image\">Resize Image</p><p name=\"crop-image\">Crop Image</p><p name=\"generate-qr-code\">Generate QR Code</p><p name=\"pdf-quick-actions\">PDF Quick Actions <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Edit, combine, organize, import/enhance PDF\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"convert-to-gif\">Convert to GIF</p><p name=\"convert-to-jpgpngsvgmp4\">Convert to JPG/PNG/SVG/MP4</p><p name=\"caption-video\">Caption Video</p><p name=\"resize-video\">Resize Video</p><p name=\"clip-maker\">Clip Maker <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Turn video podcasts, educational videos, and product reviews into social clips with captions\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"merge-crop-and-trim-video\">Merge, Crop, and Trim Video</p><p name=\"animate-characters\">Animate Characters</p></div><div name=\"brand-management-and-collaboration\"><h4>Brand management and collaboration</h4><p name=\"brand-kits\">Brand Kits <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Keep colors, fonts, logos, and graphics in one brand kit\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"extract-brand-colors-fonts-logos-from-image\">Extract brand colors, fonts, logos from image <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"One-click extraction\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"libraries\">Libraries <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Store Adobe Express and Creative Cloud assets in one place\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"branded-templates\">Branded templates <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Create brand-specific templates for teams\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"brand-controls\">Brand controls <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Specify which brand colors and fonts can be used in shared templates\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"custom-home\">Custom Home <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Branded banner and access to approved templates\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"adobe-experience-manager-integration\">Adobe Experience Manager integration <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Access, edit, and save assets back to AEM\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"custom-models\">Custom Models <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Generate on-brand content with Firefly Custom Models\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"protect-your-brand\">Protect your brand <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"IP indemnification for Adobe Firefly generated content\">ℹ️</a></p><p name=\"real-time-co-editing-and-commenting\">Real-time co-editing and commenting</p><p name=\"share-templates-across-teams\">Share templates across teams</p></div><div name=\"campaigns-and-publishing\"><h4>Campaigns and publishing</h4><p name=\"resize